          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38511693-joyce-barrass?shelf=crime">crime</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1556024203" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13348372624983001783">A well written account of this murder, with lots of interesting quotes from the original source materials. Unlike some other local murder books, this one explored an especially intriguing angle because of the author&apos;s personal family history, which includes local knowledge and her grandmother&apos;s recollection of the murderer&apos;s identity. Whether or not you agree with the author&apos;s conclusions, I am sure those local to South Yorkshire and readers of true crime will thoroughly enjoy this lively and at</span>
  <span id="freeText13348372624983001783" style="display:none">A well written account of this murder, with lots of interesting quotes from the original source materials. Unlike some other local murder books, this one explored an especially intriguing angle because of the author's personal family history, which includes local knowledge and her grandmother's recollection of the murderer's identity. Whether or not you agree with the author's conclusions, I am sure those local to South Yorkshire and readers of true crime will thoroughly enjoy this lively and at times chilling account of these tragic events in Rotherham's past.</span>
